Palp as in 
Figs 8‒11
; femur and patella not modified; tibia with retrolateral conical outgrowth (
To
) and long dorso-retrolateral apophysis (
Ta
) bifid on the tip, tibial apophysis 2.5 times longer than tibia in retrolateral view, and as long as 2/3 of cymbium; cymbium droplet shaped in dorsal view, smoothly rounded in lateral view; bulb bean-shaped in lateral view with concave ventral part, conductor (
Cd
